;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Benjicot_Blackwood\" title=\"Benjicot Blackwood\">Benjicot</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Sarra_Stark\" title=\"Sarra Stark\">Sarra<br />Stark</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Stark\" title=\"Alys Stark\">Alys<br />Stark</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Raya_Stark\" title=\"Raya Stark\">Raya<br />Stark</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Mariah_Stark\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mariah Stark\">Mariah<br />Stark</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robb_Rivers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is possible that, like other highborn bastards, he used his father's house sigil with <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Blackwood_bastard.svg\" title=\"File:House Blackwood bastard.svg\">reversed colors</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Robb and his archers were  positioned on the town walls during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"First Battle of Tumbleton\">First Battle of Tumbleton</a> before the <a href=\"/index.php/Two_Betrayers\" title=\"Two Betrayers\">Two Betrayers</a> burned it. In the aftermath of the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Battle_of_Tumbleton\" title=\"Second Battle of Tumbleton\">Second Battle of Tumbleton</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Billy_Burley\" title=\"Billy Burley\">Billy Burley</a> was considered the best archer in Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Benjicot_Blackwood\" title=\"Benjicot Blackwood\">Benjicot Blackwood</a>'s service despite Robb fighting for his family and being considered the best archer in Westeros. Therefore, Robb likely died during the First Battle of Tumbleton.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robb_Rivers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7